{"tid":2046532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★PS5 微博玩家籲買日美版　中國網民：恐怕以後沒有香港版","createTime":"2020-06-01T12:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T13:39:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7b167fafb996ea0cad684346d8f77b692d7f9f60","tid":2046532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"PlayStation 官方微博帳戶在日前為即將舉行的 PS 5 發佈會發邀請函，歡迎一眾用戶於屆時於網上收看直播。有關貼文亦隨即引來一眾中國網民及玩家的留言，當中不少人亦紛紛留言指將購買港版，而不會購買國行，甚至直言「次世代不配有國行」以及「買國行不如不買」等言論。不過，亦有網民不滿有關言論以「哪天把港版也封了就完了」及「怕以後也沒有港版」等留言作反擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/01/ps5-5/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F01%2Fps5-5%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns89g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=3e497b6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/01/ps5-5/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"beff9d603161a24f755eae266351525387731fe6","tid":2046532,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"港樓also Game Over<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25023e5d37c3cb826c38980ae0749d7b61d651dd","tid":2046532,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"日美冇中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64889f97e5db7f2a9aca16cdc19627b666e90e58","tid":2046532,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25023e5d37c3cb826c38980ae0749d7b61d651dd","tid":2046532,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"日美冇中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces